TEXT.S: Kolinda Grabar Kitarovi ryax sa tay 29 nqu tay 4, Kolinda Grabar Kitarovi , squliq na sezi'. (minhtuw sa kawas tay 1968) mrhuw Croatia ta' misuw hya' ga Kolinda Grabar Kitarovi , aring ryax tay 19 squ byacing tay 2 sa kawas 2015 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. Her presidential term ended on 18 February 2020.
